{"tid":887304,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[多片]網傳中學女生遭同學「起飛腳」毆打","createTime":"2018-11-02T19:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T22:13:38.000Z","uid":139611,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"a643fdee88f81623ec1636cf25e1be1aa3f89136","tid":887304,"uid":139611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T19:26:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/10/23/010101701.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F010101701.shtml&d=uAEzzDC6Oflb2NFRLFWiNV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=fc89fb0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2018/10/23/010101701.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門發生一宗學生遭欺凌事件，一名女生疑被女同學當街毆打，有關片段在網上廣傳。當地司警表示已接觸當事人，並已立案調查。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/17/80/10178010_800292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F17%2F80%2F10178010_800292.jpg&h=f1fe5ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女生被打倒在地上。片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n據當地傳媒報道，今日凌晨在社交網站流傳一段女生遭人毆打的短片，片段顯示，事發於晚上，身穿校服的兩名女生當時在路邊，其中一人伸腳踢中對方部，將她踢倒在地，行為粗暴。有網民留言聲稱事主是其妹，對方「唔止第一次咁樣欺凌我個妹」。<br />\n<br />\n澳門教育暨青年局表示，涉事學校於今早得悉事件後，立即通報司法警察局關注少年組，並協助家長前往報案追究，校方亦會向被打女生提供輔導。<br />\n<br />\n司警指已接觸當事人及她的監護人，並已立案偵查，司警提醒，傷害他人身體是嚴重罪行，一經定罪會被判處監禁或罰款，並留有案底，切勿以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n責編：陳正偉"},{"pid":"cd438e5799bb5c017a3ac0bb74824ec8bdc0d8bb","tid":887304,"uid":139611,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"咁踢法痛死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ce0599060b65ad97bb8947f825c9911891546b","tid":887304,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"冇人幫手？"},{"pid":"0282e3c85249f5f1f1231ff89a417e9acfc6fffc","tid":887304,"uid":139611,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1